para_trans: Madam Cama Marg, Martyrdom Rajguru Chowk
Reference: Government Order No. Usab 1324 / Q. No. 31 / Pr. 1, D. 14.10.2024.
As per the order in this regard, Mr. Pandit Khanderao Jadhav, Deputy Secretary, Rural Development Department, has been transferred from the Home Department.
2. Now, under this order, Mr. Pandit Khanderao Jadhav, Deputy Secretary, has been issued a referral order.
The post received has been partially changed and their revised post has been given as' Soil and Water Conservation '.
A vacancy is being created in the post of 'Deputy Secretary' in the department.
3. Mr. Jadhav, Deputy Secretary should immediately join the Department of Soil and Water Conservation.
4. General Administration Department, Government Circular No. Annexure-2022 / Q. 45/18 (R & AW),
Transfer of charge when the officers concerned are relieved, as mentioned in the 25.08.2022
The said Government Order is published on the website of the Government of Maharashtra www.maharashtra.gov.in.
